HEADWORD: macro lens
<hw>macro lens</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a camera lens designed to focus
at short distances so as to achieve photographic magnifications of
objects larger than with standard lenses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

